Police have used tear gas to disperse protesters blocking a bridge in Savoy, reports said.And in Bessan in southern France a frustrated driver was arrested after he took out a gun and fired in the air to try to get protesters out of the way, the Midi Libre newspaper reported.In Paris increasing numbers of protesters were gathering on the Champs-ElysÃ©es.
    
      
              
